
---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={`Projects | ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="공개 가능한 프로젝트와 글감 후보." />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <h1>Projects</h1>
      <p>블로그 글은 코드, 문서, 검증 로그와 연결되는 프로젝트를 중심으로 작성합니다.</p>
      <div class="card-grid">
        <section class="card">
          <h3>EvidenceRAG Lab</h3>
          <p>근거 기반 RAG, citation validation, claim safety scanner, public repo hygiene.</p>
        </section>
        <section class="card">
          <h3>Monkeytype privacy fork</h3>
          <p>upstream sync, privacy boundary, PWA service worker cache, Cloudflare Pages.</p>
        </section>
        <section class="card">
          <h3>Takifairy bot ops</h3>
          <p>Discord bot, local Docker production, Redis conversation context, TTS runtime.</p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
